# Google OAuth Client ID
# Obtain from: https://console.cloud.google.com → APIs & Services → Credentials
# Create an "OAuth 2.0 Client ID" of type "Web application".
# Add your Vercel deployment URL to "Authorized JavaScript origins".
# This value is a public identifier — it is NOT a secret.
#
# In Vercel: Settings → Environment Variables → add GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID
# For local dev with `vercel dev`: copy this file to .env.local and fill in the value.
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com
